    "title": "API to Booking endpoint",
    "description": "### Endpoints for Booking ###\r\n\r\n## Generating Clients ##\r\n\r\n<details><summary>In Java or C#</summary>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n### Java ###\r\n\r\n -  Download or build swagger-codegen-cli https://swagger.io/docs/open-source-tools/swagger-codegen/             \r\n -  Run \r\n        `$ java -jar swagger-codegen-cli.jar generate -l java -i https://api.matas.dk/swagger/Booking/swagger.json` \r\n -  Download [Matas HMAC Security Interceptor](/swaggergen/javahmacinterceptor)\r\n\r\nInvoke the API\r\n\r\n```\r\nimport MatasApi.HmacMatasInterceptor;\r\nimport io.swagger.client.ApiClient;\r\nimport io.swagger.client.ApiException;\r\nimport io.swagger.client.api.BookingApi;\r\nimport io.swagger.client.model.*;\r\n\r\npublic class Main {\r\n\r\n    public static void main(String[] args) throws ApiException {\r\n\r\n        ApiClient client = new ApiClient();\r\n        client.setBasePath(\"https://api.matas.dk\");\r\n\r\n        client.getHttpClient()\r\n            .interceptors()\r\n            .add(new HmacMatasInterceptor(\"<your AppId>\", \"<Shared Key>\"));\r\n\r\n        BookingApi api = new BookingApi(client);\r\n\r\n        api... <--invoke methods\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### C# ###\r\n\r\n -  Install https://github.com/RSuter/NSwag/wiki/CommandLine\r\n -  Download [Matas HMAC Base Client](/swaggergen/nswaghmacbase)\r\n -  Download [Nswag configuration](/swaggergen/nswag?filename=Booking&url=https://api.matas.dk/swagger/Booking/swagger.json)\r\n -  Generate the client\r\n    `nswag run Booking.nswag`\r\n\r\nInvoke the API\r\n\r\n```\r\nusing System;\r\nusing System.Net.Http;\r\nusing System.Threading.Tasks;\r\nusing MatasApi;\r\n\r\nclass Program\r\n{\r\n    static async Task Main(string[] args)\r\n    {\r\n        await RunAsync();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    static async Task RunAsync()\r\n    {\r\n        var client = BookingApiClient((\"<your AppId>\", \"<Shared Key\"), new HttpClient())\r\n        {\r\n            BaseUrl = \"https://api.matas.dk\"\r\n        };\r\n\r\n        var result = await client... <-- invoke methods\r\n    }\r\n} \r\n```\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n",
    "contact": {
